Back on the mat we have Dayton “The D.O.C.” O’Connor who has yet to gain a win under his belt, but is relentless as ever to hold nothing back in hopes of orgasmic filled victory. His opponent standing in his way is the undefeated Connor “The Pulverizer” Patricks. The Pulverizer believes endurance is the key to winning and plans on wearing out his opponent with his vicious leg locks. On the other hand, The D.O.C. brings his badass attitude and his scrappy fighting style to show The Pulverizer, the only key to winning is total domination. The fight heats up fast and it doesn’t take long before things get personal between these two studs as they go punch for punch and slamming each other to the mat hard. In the sex round the loser gets his face fucked before being taken back to the bathroom crawling on his hands and knees, where he’s bound to the urinals and gagged with jocks as the winner rails his ass from behind.
title: Dayton "The D.O.C." O'Connor vs Connor "The Pulverizer" Patricks
